{
  "info": {
    "name": "Aarambh AI — Developmental Digital Twin API",
    "description": "India's First Developmental Digital Twin Platform for Anganwadi children (ages 3-6).\n\nThis collection covers all v1 endpoints:\n- Auth (OTP login, JWT)\n- Children (CRUD, DDT)\n- Attendance (batch mark)\n- Observations (voice, text)\n- Milestones (library, assessment)\n- PDRS (compute, history)\n- Drawings (upload, Crayon Intelligence™)\n- Referrals (generate, letter, notify)\n- Recommendations (AI activities)\n- Dashboard (AWW, CDPO, Heatmap)\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Run the Start application workflow\n2. Call POST /auth/request-otp with any phone number\n3. Copy the OTP from the response\n4. Call POST /auth/verify-otp — the access_token is auto-saved\n5. All other requests use Bearer auth automatically\n\n**Variables:** BASE_URL defaults to http://0.0.0.0:8000/api/v1",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "aarambh-ai-v1-collection"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "BASE_URL",
      "value": "http://0.0.0.0:8000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "TOKEN",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "CHILD_ID",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "AWC_ID",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "REFERRAL_ID",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "DRAWING_ID",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{TOKEN}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Request OTP",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.otp) { console.log('Dev OTP:', json.otp); }"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"+919876543210\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/request-otp",
              "host": [
                "{{BASE_URL}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "request-otp"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify OTP (get token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.access_token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('TOKEN', json.access_token); }",
                  "if (json.user && json.user.id) { console.log('Logged in as:', json.user.name, '|', json.user.role); }"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"+919876543210\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/verify-otp",
              "host": [
                "{{BASE_URL}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "verify-otp"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Current User (/me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/me",
              "host": [
                "{{BASE_URL}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "me"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.access_token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('TOKEN', json.access_token); }"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/refresh",
              "host": [
                "{{BASE_URL}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "refresh"
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
